Package ptolemy.homer.gui

The ptolemy/homer/gui package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeTreeModel
    A tree model for Ptolemy II models.
    HomerMainFrame
    The container window for the UI designer that maintains the palette of placeable elements of the model, widget references, and the tabs/scene placement.
    HomerMenu
    Menu for supporting the layout builder application.
    NamedObjectTree
    A side panel panel containing tree of named objects, filtering text field and draggable label.
    OpenLayoutDialog
    Customized dialog for opening models and their layouts.
    RemoteObjectList
    A list of the model components that will be run remotely.
    SizeDialog
    Class that defines the screen size dialog.
    TabbedLayoutScene
    The tabbed panel that contains the scenes onto which widgets can be dropped by the user in order to construct a layout for a particular model file.
    TabScenePanel
    The tab scene onto which widgets can be dropped, resized, and arranged in order to suite the needs of the handheld consumer.
    WidgetPropertiesFrame
    The property window for setting widget position and size.

Package ptolemy.homer.gui Description

The ptolemy/homer/gui package.

Ptolemy II 8.1
